tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE neural_network_performance_metrics (
    metric_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    metric_name VARCHAR(100),
    metric_value FLOAT,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE neural_networks (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    name VARCHAR(255),
    layers INT,
    activation_function VARCHAR(50)
)

CREATE TABLE performance_metrics (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    neural_network_id INT,
    metric_name VARCHAR(100),
    metric_value FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE reports (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    report_date DATE,
    neural_network_id INT,
    metric_id INT
)

CREATE TABLE decision_making (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    report_id INT,
    decision VARCHAR(255)
)

CREATE TABLE NeuralNetworkMetrics (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    network_name VARCHAR(50),
    date_recorded DATE,
    metric_type VARCHAR(50),
    metric_value FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE DashboardUsers (
    user_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    username VARCHAR(50),
    email VARCHAR(100),
    role VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE DashboardVisualizations (
    visualization_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    visualization_type VARCHAR(50),
    data_source VARCHAR(100),
    creation_date DATE,
    author VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE ReportPerformance (
    report_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    report_name VARCHAR(100),
    report_type VARCHAR(50),
    created_by VARCHAR(50),
    creation_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE DecisionMakingLogs (
    log_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    action VARCHAR(100),
    user_id INT,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    notes TEXT
);
